40OM_uint32 GSSAPI_CALLCONV
41_gss_ntlm_inquire_sec_context_by_oid(OM_uint32 *minor_status,
42 gss_const_ctx_id_t context_handle,
43 const gss_OID desired_object,
44 gss_buffer_set_t *data_set)
45{
46 ntlm_ctx ctx = (ntlm_ctx)context_handle;
47
48 if (ctx == NULL) {
49 *minor_status = 0;
50 return GSS_S_NO_CONTEXT;
51 }
52
53 if (gss_oid_equal(desired_object, GSS_NTLM_GET_SESSION_KEY_X) ||
54 gss_oid_equal(desired_object, GSS_C_INQ_SSPI_SESSION_KEY)) {
55 gss_buffer_desc value;
56
57 value.length = ctx->sessionkey.length;
58 value.value = ctx->sessionkey.data;
59
60 return gss_add_buffer_set_member(minor_status,
61 &value,
62 data_set);
63 } else if (gss_oid_equal(desired_object, GSS_C_INQ_WIN2K_PAC_X)) {
64 if (ctx->pac.length == 0) {
65 *minor_status = ENOENT;
66 return GSS_S_FAILURE;
67 }
68
69 return gss_add_buffer_set_member(minor_status,
70 &ctx->pac,
71 data_set);
72
73 } else if (gss_oid_equal(desired_object, GSS_C_NTLM_AVGUEST)) {
74 gss_buffer_desc value;
75 uint32_t num;
76
77 if (ctx->kcmflags & KCM_NTLM_FLAG_AV_GUEST)
78 num = 1;
79 else
80 num = 0;
81
82 value.length = sizeof(num);
83 value.value = &num;
84
85 return gss_add_buffer_set_member(minor_status,
86 &value,
87 data_set);
88 } else {
89 *minor_status = 0;
90 return GSS_S_FAILURE;
91 }
92}
